cast.overview: A teenager with no memory of his past finds himself among a group of boys living in a walled enclosure surrounded by a massive, ever-changing maze. As he struggles to adapt to their rules and society, he begins to uncover clues that may lead to escape and the truth behind their confinement.
cast.title: The Maze Runner

details.biography: Jerry Clark is an actor from the Southeastern region of the United States. He has most recently been featured in the feature film, "The Maze Runner", and TV pilot, "Help Wanted". Jerry has also worked with Saint Studios as an assistant DOP and PA. Jerry is pursuing his degree in Theatre Performance and minor in Dance at the University of Southern Mississippi while working on various independent film projects. Jerry's experience is not limited to acting; he has toured with the Memphis Pop Punk band, The Vital Society, and has collaborated on music projects with Universal Motown's Forever the Sickest Kids.  - IMDb Mini Biography
details.name: Jerry Clark
